request.doc:
To create an IPv4 address:
POST https://{appliance_hostname}/isam/application_interfaces/{interface_id}/addresses
POST_DATA: { "enabled":"true/false", "mode4":"static/auto", "address":"ipv4 address", "netmask":"subnet mask", "type":"ipv4" }
To create an IPv6 address:
POST https://{appliance_hostname}/isam/application_interfaces/{interface_id}/addresses
POST_DATA: { "enabled":"true/false", "address":"ipv6 address", "prefix":"ipv6 prefix", "type":"ipv6" }
